<item>
            <title>[CXF-6711] Aegis Databinding Deserialization Vulnerability</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-6711</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Just had a quick look after the topic came up on -users. Aegis Databiding seems to perform unsafe deserialization when serializedWhenUnknown=true. Now sure how common that is (and actually no experience with aegis at all), but if used and enabled that&apos;s pretty much direct remote code execution.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12922030">CXF-6711</key>
            <summary>Aegis Databinding Deserialization Vulnerability</summary>
